# Prompt Engineering System: Quick Reference Guide

> [!abstract] Purpose
> One-page reference for daily workflow operations. Keep this open while working.

---

## ‚ö° QUICK OPERATIONS

### Create New Prompt (Full Template)
1. `Ctrl+P` ‚Üí "Templater: Create new note from template"
2. Select template type (System/User/Chain/Component/etc.)
3. Answer guided questions
4. Template auto-populates metadata and structure
‚è±Ô∏è **Time**: 2-5 minutes

### Quick Capture Idea (Minimal)
1. `Ctrl+P` ‚Üí "QuickAdd: Prompt Quick Capture"
2. Enter: Title ‚Üí Type ‚Üí Initial notes
3. Saved to `00-inbox/prompt-ideas/`
‚è±Ô∏è **Time**: <10 seconds

### Search & Insert Component
1. Place cursor where you want component
2. `Ctrl+P` ‚Üí "QuickAdd: Component Search & Insert"
3. Type keyword ‚Üí Select from results
4. Component text inserted
‚è±Ô∏è **Time**: <15 seconds

---

## üìã COMMON WORKFLOWS

### Create System Prompt
**Template**: `_system-prompt-creator.md`
**Sections**: Role ‚Üí Context ‚Üí Task ‚Üí Constraints ‚Üí Format ‚Üí Examples
**Components to Consider**: Personas, Instructions, Output Formats

### Create Few-Shot Prompt
**Template**: `_few-shot-template.md`
**Structure**: 2-5 input/output pairs + pattern notes
**Best Practice**: Show reasoning in examples

### Build Prompt Chain
**Template**: `_prompt-chain-builder.md`
**Key**: Define context handoff between turns
**Integration**: Links to SPES sequential workflows

### A/B Test Prompts
**Template**: `_ab-test-template.md`
**Process**: Define criteria ‚Üí Run variants ‚Üí Score ‚Üí Select winner
**Location**: Save in `05-testing-validation/ab-tests/`

### Debug Failing Prompt
**Template**: `_debug-template.md`
**Method**: Describe issue ‚Üí Hypothesize ‚Üí Test ‚Üí Document solution
**Tip**: Check component conflicts first

