## üîß PLUGIN SYNTAX CHEAT SHEET

### Templater Basics
```javascript
// User input (text)
<% await tp.system.prompt("Question?", "Default") %>

// User selection (dropdown)
<% await tp.system.suggester(
    ["Display 1", "Display 2"],
    ["value1", "value2"],
    false,
    "Choose:"
) %>

// Current date/time
<% tp.date.now("YYYY-MM-DD") %>
<% tp.date.now("YYYYMMDDHHmmss") %>

// File operations
<% tp.file.title %>
<% tp.file.folder(true) %>

// Cursor placement
<% tp.file.cursor() %>
```

### Meta-Bind Basics
```markdown
<!-- View field (read-only) -->
`VIEW[{field-name}]`

<!-- Input fields -->
`INPUT[text:field-name]`
`INPUT[number:field-name]`
`INPUT[toggle:field-name]`
`INPUT[slider(min(1), max(10)):rating]`
`INPUT[suggester(option(Low), option(Med), option(High)):priority]`

<!-- Button -->
`BUTTON[button-id]`
```

### Dataview Basics
```dataview
TABLE status, rating, modified
FROM "02-component-library"
WHERE type = "component"
SORT rating DESC
LIMIT 20
```

### DataviewJS Basics
```dataviewjs
const prompts = dv.pages('"08-active-prompts"')
    .where(p => p.type === "system")
    .sort(p => p.rating, 'desc');

dv.table(
    ["Prompt", "Rating", "Status"],
    prompts.map(p => [p.file.link, p.rating, p.status])
);
```

