## üìä METADATA FIELD REFERENCE

### Required Fields
```yaml
type: "prompt" | "component" | "workflow"
id: "20251220123456"
status: "active" | "testing" | "production" | "deprecated"
version: "1.0.0"
created: "YYYY-MM-DD"
modified: "YYYY-MM-DD"
```

### Quality Fields
```yaml
rating: 0.0-10.0
confidence: "speculative" | "provisional" | "moderate" | "established" | "high"
maturity: "seedling" | "developing" | "budding" | "evergreen"
usage-count: 0
last-used: "[[YYYY-MM-DD]]"
```

### Review Fields (Spaced Repetition)
```yaml
review-next: "YYYY-MM-DD"
review-interval: 7  # days
review-count: 0
```

### Categorization
```yaml
tags:
  - "year/2025"
  - "prompt-engineering"
  - "llm-capability/generation"
aliases: ["Alt Name 1", "Alt Name 2"]
link-up: "[[prompt-engineering-moc]]"
link-related: ["[[related-1]]", "[[related-2]]"]
```

