## üö® TROUBLESHOOTING

### Template Not Working
1. Check Templater is enabled
2. Verify template path is correct
3. Check for syntax errors (missing `%>`)
4. Test with simple template first

### Component Not Inserting
1. Verify component file exists in library
2. Check file name matches exactly (case-sensitive)
3. Ensure component has proper frontmatter
4. Try manual `![[component-name]]` link

### Dataview Query Empty
1. Check folder path in FROM clause
2. Verify WHERE conditions match metadata
3. Test with simpler query first
4. Check Dataview plugin is enabled

### Metadata Not Validating
1. Check YAML syntax (no tabs, proper indentation)
2. Verify field names match schema exactly
3. Check for trailing spaces in values
4. Use Meta-Bind suggester for controlled fields

### QuickAdd Macro Not Running
1. Check JavaScript syntax in macro file
2. Verify macro is registered in QuickAdd settings
3. Check console for error messages (`Ctrl+Shift+I`)
4. Test with simple macro first

---

## üí° BEST PRACTICES

### When Creating Prompts
‚úÖ Use templates (consistent structure)
‚úÖ Search components first (reuse > recreate)
‚úÖ Add examples (few-shot improves quality)
‚úÖ Test before deploying (catch issues early)
‚úÖ Version significant changes (track evolution)

‚ùå Don't skip metadata (breaks queries)
‚ùå Don't hardcode common patterns (use components)
‚ùå Don't delete old versions (archive instead)
‚ùå Don't forget to log test results

### When Building Components
‚úÖ Keep atomic (single purpose)
‚úÖ Document when/when-not to use
‚úÖ Include usage examples
‚úÖ Test in multiple contexts
‚úÖ Track performance data

### When Testing
‚úÖ Define success criteria first
‚úÖ Document all results (positive and negative)
‚úÖ Compare against baseline
‚úÖ Track quality scores consistently
‚úÖ Extract patterns from failures

