## üéì LEARNING PATH

### Day 1: Foundation
1. Create first prompt with master template
2. Quick capture 2-3 ideas
3. Browse component library
4. View main dashboard

### Week 1: Core Workflows
1. Create system prompt with components
2. Build few-shot examples
3. Try A/B test on one prompt
4. Explore specialized templates

### Month 1: Advanced Usage
1. Build prompt chain
2. Extract successful patterns to library
3. Use analytics to find improvements
4. Optimize low-performing prompts

